nodes.text: Marvel Super Special 27: Return of the Jedi
Marvel Super Special 27: Return of the Jedi collects all four issues of the Star Wars: Return of the Jedi series.
This is a complete comic book adaptation of Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi.
It was misspelled as "Super Special 26" in the second issue of Marvel Age, which also was in charge of providing its release date for the Coming Attractions section.
